					<div class="bio mollyford">
						<div class="bio-title">
							<span>Molly Ford<span>
						</div>
						<div class="bio-content">
							<p>Molly is a leading authority in branding, advertising, and efficient consumer targeting. Also, Ms. Ford has a depth and range of experience in new media, social networking to traditional broadcast (radio and TV), print (magazines &amp; news) and online marketing. Molly was a founding officer of Disney Infoseek, as well as AOL, and was Chief Integration Officer of Netscape. </p>
							<p>Molly was the highest ranking business woman executive at US News &amp; World Report, Business Week and Time. She was a leading executive at Time Warner and led executive teams in many consumer related businesses. Ms. Ford started her career in her family's international multi-format retailing and distribution businesses. She has served on the boards of various educational, philanthropic and business institutions.</p>
