						<div class="bio-content">
							<p>Sturgess has over 25 years experience in classic food distribution, &quot;on premise&quot; gourmet, specialty, and traditional food &amp; beverage businesses. Sturgess was Operating Partner at JSS/Old Yankee Beverage, the largest fine wine &amp; spirit distributor &amp; retailer in Northern New England. He was National Sales Manager for Fossil Farms' specialty gourmet meats and national &amp; international fresh products portfolio. As National Accounts Manager for San Pelligrino, Pana &amp; Nestle Waters, he helped establish these brands as leaders in the &ldquo;on premise&rdquo;, retail, wholesale, food service &amp; consumer sales categories.</p>
							<p>Throughout his career, Sturgess has worked with some the best distributors, retailers, wholesalers, restaurants, and consumer brand companies across the globe. Sturgess has also worked with a broad range of SRG clients, including: Agri Beef, Ahold USA, U.S. Foodservice &amp; due diligence work for various private equity firms, on Kings, et al.</p>
